FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://MyDiary-v2.herokuapp.com

# MyDiary

MyDiary is an online journal where users can pen down their thoughts
and feelings.

## UserSignup Collection [/api/v1/user/signup]

### Signup [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    {
        "username":"Belinda", 
        "email":"belinda@gmail.com",
        "password":"mypassword"
    }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /api/v1/user/signup

    + Body

        {
            "message": "Successfully registered",
            "user": {
                "username": "Belinda",
                "email": "belinda@gmail.com",
                "id": 628
            }
        }

