## Entry Creation Collection [/api/v1/user/entries]

### Add Entry [POST]

+ Request  (application/json)

        {
            "title" : "My demo",
            "description" : "This is for demonstration"
        }

+ Headers

            Location: /api/v1/user/entries

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

                Location: /api/va/user/entries

    + Body

            {
                "message": "Entry has been published",
                "entry": [
                    {
                        "created_at": "2018-07-27T19:43:42.427841",
                        "last_modified": "2018-07-27T19:43:42.427864",
                        "title": "My demo",
                        "user_id": 628,
                        "description": "This is for demonstration",
                        "id": 164
                    }
                ]
            }

