## Modify Entry Collection [/api/v1/user/entries/165]

### Modify Entry [PUT]

+ Request  (application/json)

        {
            "title" : "My demo",
            "description" : "This is for demonstration"
        }

+ Headers

            Location: /api/v1/user/entries/165

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

                Location: /api/va/user/entries

    + Body

            {
                "message": "Entry updated successfully",
                "new_entry": {
                    "created_at": "2018-07-27T19:54:14.774072",
                    "last_modified": "2018-07-27T19:54:14.774107",
                    "title": "The day was lovely",
                    "user_id": 628,
                    "description": "Oh what a day it was",
